name: Simple-DankGrinder
description: A really simple Dank Grinder self bot which can bypass account bans

channelID.description: Channel ID of channel in which you want the selfbot to send messages. Youtube Video : https://youtu.be/NLWtSHWKbAI

storageAccount.description: The account on which you want to tranfer your dank coins. Put selfbot's id if you dont want to transfer !

timezone.description: Your timezone. You can get it here : https://webbrowsertools.com/timezone/ ; e.g. Asia/Calcutta

endTime.description: Time when you want the bot to stop working e.g. 19; Use 24 hr format and put only the hour value !! ( Recommended difference between start and end time is 12 hrs )

startTime.description: Time when you want the bot to start running e.g. 7; Use 24 hr format and put only the hour value !! ( Recommended difference between start and end time is 12 hrs )

token.description: Grinder Account Token e.g. OTQ1OTI5MjExNDIyNjAxMjE2.YhXTcQ.f8W2BsaUHjsahdQWfq-OKASDHKhWQ; Youtube Video : https://youtu.be/YEgFvgg7ZPI

autoSell.description: Whether you want to autoSell or not ! You can only put 'true' or 'false'; e.g. true
